The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, martial-arts, zombie
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, snooker, chess
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, lizard
 1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the bartender and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the designer is the person playing poker##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the project-manager is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the person playing snooker is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | social-worker | bartender | designer | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | zombie    | crime    | martial-arts    |
| Game   | monopoly        | chess   | poker   | snooker         |
| Pet           | goat          | dog       | lizard   | horse           |

